@startuml
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
interface Customer {
  #long code
  #String active
  -float amount
  +long duration
  +getDescription()
  +createScore()
}
abstract class Branch {
  -boolean code
  #long email
  +calculateQuantity()
  +processQuantity()
}
abstract class Teller {
  +int note
  -boolean quantity
  -String score
  +getDuration()
  +findEmail()
}
abstract class Statement {
  +String type
  #String address
  -Date score
  -String updatedAt
  +long code
  +setScore()
}
Statement --> Customer : "0..1"
Teller --|> Statement
Branch --* Teller
note right of Customer : Banking domain
@enduml